26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_i2c_padnv04.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:34 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "pad.h"
30#include "bus.h"
31
32static const struct nvkm_i2c_pad_func
33nv04_i2c_pad_func = {
34 .bus_new_0 = nv04_i2c_bus_new,
35};
36
37int
38nv04_i2c_pad_new(struct nvkm_i2c *i2c, int id, struct nvkm_i2c_pad **ppad)
39{
40 return nvkm_i2c_pad_new_(&nv04_i2c_pad_func, i2c, id, ppad);
41}
